trans-unit.source: Provides a design-time data bindings editor in a design host, such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvsext](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], for a <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.TreeViewDesigner"></xref> object.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.TreeViewBindingsEditor"></xref> class.
